{{Infobox journal | title = Revue des études byzantines | cover = | former_name = Échos d'Orient, Études byzantines | abbreviation = Rev. études byz. | discipline = [[Classical studies|Classical]] and [[oriental studies]] | language = English, French, German, Italian, Spanish | editor = Olivier Delouis | publisher = [[Peeters (publishing company)|Peeters]] on behalf of the [[Institut Catholique de Paris]] | country = | history = 1897-present | frequency = Annually | openaccess = | license = | impact = | impact-year = | ISSN = 0771-3347 | eISSN = 0771-3444 | CODEN = | JSTOR = | LCCN = | OCLC = 781579014 | website = http://www.icp.fr/recherche/chaires-et-instituts/institut-francais-d-etudes-byzantines-ifeb-/revue-des-etudes-byzantines-1271.kjsp?RH=11429522327430-1236 | link1 = http://poj.peeters-leuven.be/content.php?url=journal&journal_code=REB | link1-name = Online access | link2 = http://www.persee.fr/collection/rebyz | link2-name = Online archive }} [[File:Échos d'Orient.PNG|thumb|''Échos d'Orient'', 1903]] The '''''Revue des études byzantines''''' is an annual [[peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] covering the study of [[Greek Christianity]] and especially [[Byzantine civilization]]. It was established in 1897 as '''''Échos d'Orient''''', renamed '''''Études byzantines''''' in (with volume numbering re-starting at 1), and obtaining its current title in 1946.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://poj.peeters-leuven.be/content.php?url=journal&journal_code=REB |title=Revue des Études Byzantines |website=PEETERS ONLINE JOURNALS |publisher=Peeters |accessdate=14 July 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.persee.fr/collection/rebyz |title=Revue des études byzantines |publisher=[[Persée (web portal)|Persée]] |accessdate=14 July 2016}}</ref> The journal is published by [[Peeters (publishing company)|Peeters]] on behalf of the [[Institut Catholique de Paris]] and the [[editor-in-chief]] is Olivier Delouis.
